{"tid":606161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 無厘頭變「TVB最受歡迎」港醫生：內地醫生寶號咪盡信","createTime":"2018-03-26T09:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T09:20:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd5fc48eec32088a888c39d78b2fd9a3dc9c8cf","tid":606161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180326/20342863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F20342863&d=lB94GkTWBmGCjNDwVyBISL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6fafcb9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F20342863&h=59106444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180326/20342863</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n無厘頭變「TVB最受歡迎」港醫生：內地醫生寶號咪盡信<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n時下整容成風，更有不少愛美之心會北上深圳「修理」臉容。《蘋果》記者上月底暗訪深圳兩間富有聲譽、港人推薦的整形醫院，發現醫院上的水牌排列出所有醫生的專業「頭銜」，可是他們的專業資格難以求證。有香港醫生認為內地機構對醫生的監管較鬆散，她多年前在內地教授注射透明質酸時，在醫院大堂驚見自己的易拉架廣告，上面寫着「TVB最受歡迎整形外科醫生」、「全英國最佳華人醫生」等頭銜，呼籲消費者到內地整容時勿盡信內地宣傳品。<br />\n<br />\n記者周凱瑩<br />\n<br />\n攝影王心義"},{"pid":"9ca6eace2d23bf7d406c39305e1e1a268fad29fb","tid":606161,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}